<img src="https://i0.wp.com/837274.smushcdn.com/1798008/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rotimikeys_Life-Is-Beautiful_AlbumArt-420x420.png?ssl=1" data-recalc-dims="1" /> Rotimikeys Rotimikeys' new single, Life is Beautiful is the perfect mix of cool afro-pop, feel-good vibes and musical delight. While most listeners will connect and sway to the rhythm, many will break a dance step or two. A renowned Producer, Arranger,  and Music Director, Rotimikeys is fast building his profile as a singer.This track is coming after the  2017 release of his celebrated  EP Wild Colours,  a cover of top songs by some Nigeria's iconic artistes in versatile Afro-funk, Jazz and Pop styles. 2020 has been a tough year with the Covid-19 pandemic amongst other global issues and Life is Beautiful reminds all that things will get better in time and we will smile again. Released in May 2020, the track is available for streaming  and downloads. GET THE AUDIO HEREhttp://rotimikeys.ffm.to/life_is_beautiful The post Rotimikeys – Life is Beautiful appeared first on Latest Naija Nigerian Music, Songs & Video – Notjustok. Original Article Get all the Latest news, Breaking headlines,Sport, Education, Finance, Gists, Jobs, Music/Video, Technology and Top stories in real time in Nigeria and around the world.